{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 2b shows the sentiment distribution for each topic.",
    "The breakdown of distribution statistics is available in table 3.",
    "We obtained further evidence on both public concern and enthusiasm regarding the use of ChatGPT, showing that AI's effects on education and writing are perceived as negative.",
    "Inversely, ChatGPT was mostly discussed in a positive way in image generation, financial, and technical conversations.",
    "Nonetheless, the widespread sentiment distribution is common to all the extracted topics and underlines the potential controversy it generated in the public debate."
  ]
}